Executive Profile
Richard C. Gozon BAOperating Partner and Lead Independent Director, Atlas Holdings LLCAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 9 different industries.See Board Relationships78--
Background

		Mr. Richard C. Gozon, BA, serves as an Operating Partner of Atlas Holdings LLC. At Atlas Holdings LLC, Mr. Gozon focuses on building materials industry. He has an industry expertise in the distribution, energy and forest products sectors of over 40 years. Mr. Gozon served as an Executive Vice President at Weyerhaeuser Co, from June 1994 to April, 2002. He served as the President and Chief Operating Officer at Alco Standard Corporation from 1988 to 1993. He served as ... an Executive Vice President and Chief Operating Officer at Paper Corporation of America since 1988 and served as its President from 1979 to 1987. He served as a Vice President at Paper Corporation of America from 1982 to 1988. Mr. Gozon served as the Chairman of board for AmerisourceBergen Corp. since February 9, 2006 until March 3, 2016. He serves as a Member of the Board of Managers of AGI Global Holdings Cooperatief U.A. and Atlas AGI Holdings LLC. He serves as Lead Independent Director of Atlas Holdings LLC. He has been a Director at AmeriGas Eagle Finance Corp. since February 24, 1998. He has been a Director of Amerisourcebergen Corp. from August 2001. He serves as a Member of the Board of Trustees of Thomas Jefferson University. Mr. Gozon serves as member of the Board of Managers of the ASG Group. He served as Lead Independent Director at Triumph Group, Inc. until July 20, 2017 and served as its Independent Director since 1993 until July 20, 2017. He served as a Director and Presiding Director of AmeriGas Propane, Inc., a General Partner of AP Eagle Finance Corp. and AmeriGas Partners LP from February 24, 1998 to January 20, 2011. He served as a Director of UGI Utilities Inc. from 1989 to January 20, 2011. He served as Director of Alco Standard Corporation from 1984 to 1993. He served as a Director of AmeriGas Propane L.P. He served as a Director of UGI Corp. since 1989 and also served as its Presiding Director. He served as a Director of AmeriSource Health Corporation from 1994 to August 2001. He served as the Chairman of Nippon Paper Industries, from June 1994 to 2002 and Norpac (North Pacific Paper Company) since 1994. Mr. Gozon holds a BA degree from Valparasio University.Read Full Background




